  m_text: "<align=center><size=200%>Chat Demo</size></align>\n\nThis demo allows
    you to chat with a LLM while retaining conversation history, meaning you can
    ask for details about the previous messages. \n<i>( The history is lost between
    Plays) </i>\nAdditionally, the response is streamed in chunks. <i>( <b>i.e.</b>
    words by words)</i>\nCheck the code of the buffer queue for how to handle the
    callbacks."
